apt-mirror (0.6.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rewrite in Python with async support
  * Add diff serving capability using xdelta3
  * Improve error handling and progress reporting
  * Add automatic retry with exponential backoff
  * Add resume partial downloads support
  * Add checksum verification option
  * Backward compatible with existing mirror.list configuration
  * All dependencies available in Debian/Ubuntu repositories

 -- Debian/Ubuntu Maintainers <debian-apt-mirror@lists.debian.org>  Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000

